column2: select DISTINCT top # s.objID, s.psfMag_u - s.extinction_u as u, s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g as g, s.psfMag_r - s.extinction_R as r, s.psfMag_i - s.extinction_i as i, s.psfMag_z - s.extinction_z as z, s.psfMagErr_u as u_err, s.psfMagErr_g as g_err, s.psfMagErr_r as r_err, s.psfMagErr_i as i_err, s.psfMagErr_z as z_err, s.ra, s.dec, s.raErr as ra_err, s.decErr as dec_err from (SELECT dec, row_number() over (order by dec) as rownum FROM star ) as s where s.rownum % # = # AND s.CLEAN = # AND s.ra BETWEEN # AND # AND s.dec BETWEEN # AND # AND  s.psfMag_r < # AND s.psfMag_g < # order by s.dec ASC
